QuestData.Title: Sticky Situation
QuestData.Description: A squadron of arakkoa spotted us while we were en route to the excavation site and took out our caravan. My brother made it to safety in the chaos.$B$BLucky son of a tinker.$B$BI can't leave without the batteries for our drill, but they all fell into the bog and I can't even get them to budge.$B$BAny chance you could retrieve them for me?
